This mutator allows you to configure:

- Max Dmg
- InventoryGroup
- Max Ammo
- Magazine Size
- Ammo Cost
- Cost
- Weight
- Impact Dmg ( For Rocket Launchers / Demo Weapons )
- ProjPerFire
- HeadShot multiplier
- Spread
- Reload Speed
- Reload Animation Speed
- Fire Rate
- Fire Rate Animation speed

Of all weapons. Custom or Official!

- [url=https://github.com/Vel-San/KF-WeaponStatConfig/commits/master]Track My Progress Here[/url]


[H1][b][u]Number Of Files[/u][/b][/H1]

- 3

[H1][b][u]File Names[/u][/b][/H1]

- \System\WeaponStatConfig.u
- \System\WeaponStatConfig.ucl
- \System\WeaponStat_Config.ini

[H1][b][u]Usage[/u][/b][/H1]

1- Subscribe or download manually (recommended)
2- Launch the game and wait to see 'Completed'
3- Restart the game and you can see the mutators in your list
4- Before you start your server, navigate to your directory and edit the configuration file. Add/Remove whatever weapon you want. Follow instructions in the config file to understand what each value does.

Sample config can be as the following:

- [url=https://github.com/Bleeding-Action-Man/WeaponStatConfig/blob/master/Config/WeaponStat_Config.ini]Config File[/url]

[code]
All KF Weapon Classes (Some might be not found or removed by TWI)

https://pastebin.com/StRzZntT
[/code]

[H1][b][u]Class Names[/u][/b][/H1]

- WeaponStatConfig.WeaponStatConfig

